UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;

float u_xlat29;

bool u_xlatb33;
float u_xlat34;
bool u_xlatb34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat38;
bool u_xlatb38;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_35;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb38 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb38 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlatb34 || u_xlatb38;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb34) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = abs(u_xlat16_36) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_4.xxx) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_41 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_7 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat7.x = log2(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat7.x = exp2(u_xlat7.x);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat38) * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat29 * u_xlat29 + u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_13.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat18.x = min(u_xlat18.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat18.xxx;
    u_xlat18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_41 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_37 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_37 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_2.x));
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat34 + (-u_xlat38);
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat11 * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat34 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat33 * u_xlat11 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_13.x * 0.5;
    u_xlat22 = (-u_xlat39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat22 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat33 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat22) * u_xlat33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat22 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb33 = !!(u_xlat22<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb33 = u_xlat22<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xy = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat22 + -2.0;
        u_xlat22 = (u_xlatb33) ? u_xlat22 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb22 = !!(u_xlat22<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb22 = u_xlat22<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb22) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_9.y;
        u_xlati22 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati22].xyz;
        u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat34 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat34;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati22].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati22].xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;

    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat34<u_xlat6.z;
    u_xlat6.x = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat34<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.y = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.0 : 1.0;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTexShoe;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNrShoe;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
float u_xlat11;
uint u_xlatu11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat18;
float u_xlat22;
int u_xlati22;
bool u_xlatb22;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat29;
float u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb33;
float u_xlat34;
bool u_xlatb34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat38;
bool u_xlatb38;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_35;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb38 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb38 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlatb34 || u_xlatb38;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb34) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = abs(u_xlat16_36) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_4.xxx) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_41 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_7 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat7.x = log2(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat7.x = exp2(u_xlat7.x);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat38) * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat29 * u_xlat29 + u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_13.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat18.x = min(u_xlat18.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat18.xxx;
    u_xlat18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_41 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_37 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_37 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_2.x));
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat34 + (-u_xlat38);
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat11 * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat34 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat33 * u_xlat11 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_13.x * 0.5;
    u_xlat22 = (-u_xlat39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat22 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat33 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat22) * u_xlat33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);

    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat22 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb33 = !!(u_xlat22<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb33 = u_xlat22<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xy = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat22 + -2.0;
        u_xlat22 = (u_xlatb33) ? u_xlat22 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb22 = !!(u_xlat22<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb22 = u_xlat22<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb22) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_9.y;
        u_xlati22 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati22].xyz;
        u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat34 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat34;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati22].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati22].xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;

    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);

    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;

        u_xlat22 = (u_xlatb33) ? u_xlat22 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb22 = u_xlat22<1.0;
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb22) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_9.y;
        u_xlati22 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).xyz;
        u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat34 = float(1.0) / u_xlat33;
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).y;
        u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat34;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).w;
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati22).xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat21;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTexShoe;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNrShoe;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;

in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;

uint u_xlatu11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat18;
float u_xlat22;
int u_xlati22;
bool u_xlatb22;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat29;
float u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb33;
float u_xlat34;
bool u_xlatb34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat38;
bool u_xlatb38;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;

vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat21;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat34<u_xlat6.z;
    u_xlat6.x = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat34<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.y = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat34<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.z = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlat34<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.w = (u_xlatb34) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlatb34 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb38 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlatb34 || u_xlatb38;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb34) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = abs(u_xlat16_36) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_4.xxx) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_41 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_7 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat10_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;

    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;

float u_xlat11;
uint u_xlatu11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat18;
float u_xlat22;
int u_xlati22;
bool u_xlatb22;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat29;
float u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb33;
float u_xlat34;
bool u_xlatb34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat38;
bool u_xlatb38;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_13.x = max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(u_xlat16_13.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_24 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_35;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb34 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb34 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb38 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb38 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb34 = u_xlatb34 || u_xlatb38;
    u_xlat16_24 = (u_xlatb34) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_35) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat33) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = abs(u_xlat16_36) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat38 = min(max(u_xlat38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat38 = clamp(u_xlat38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_4.xxx) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_41 = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_7 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat7.x = log2(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat7.x = exp2(u_xlat7.x);
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat7.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat38) * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat38;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat29 * u_xlat29 + u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_13.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat18.x = min(u_xlat18.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat18.xxx;
    u_xlat18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat7.xxx;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_36) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_41 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_37 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_37 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_2.x));
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat38 * u_xlat34 + (-u_xlat38);
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat11 * u_xlat38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat34 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_13.x) * u_xlat16_13.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat33 * u_xlat11 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat16_13.x * 0.5;
    u_xlat22 = (-u_xlat39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat22 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat33 * u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat22) * u_xlat33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_24);

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11 * u_xlat16_2.x;

    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb33 = !!(u_xlat22<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb33 = u_xlat22<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xy = (bool(u_xlatb33)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat22 + -2.0;
        u_xlat22 = (u_xlatb33) ? u_xlat22 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb22 = !!(u_xlat22<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb22 = u_xlat22<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb22) ? u_xlat16_9.x : u_xlat16_9.y;
        u_xlati22 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati22].xyz;

        u_xlat33 = max(u_xlat33, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat34 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat33);
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat34;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati22].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati22].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati22].xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;

    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];

    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _HairMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _BumpMapNr2_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Mask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _colorSkin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowPow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShift;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _faceshadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainPlayerPositionWS;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat21;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

#extension GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod : enable
#endif

precision highp float;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
