	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowPow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShiftOffuse2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SunShift;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_1Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _specularColor2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2X;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _glossiness_2Y;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _shapeST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _faceshadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FresnelColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FresnelFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainPlayerPositionWS;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MatColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
bool u_xlatb35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = abs(u_xlat16_32) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_22.y = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4 = max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4 = min(u_xlat16_4, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_4) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_14 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_31) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_22.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_4) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_22.x = clamp(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4 + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat30 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat30 = exp2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat4, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb35 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb35 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb35 = u_xlatb35 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_31 = (u_xlatb35) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_11 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_12 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat21;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
bool u_xlatb35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = abs(u_xlat16_32) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_22.y = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4 = max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4 = min(u_xlat16_4, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_4) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_14 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_31) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_22.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_4) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_22.x = clamp(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4 + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat30 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat30 = exp2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat4, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb35 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb35 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb35 = u_xlatb35 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_31 = (u_xlatb35) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_11 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_ALPHATEST_ON" "_ATVECTOR_X" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHADOWS_SOFT" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{

    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;

    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_12 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;

    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12 + _RimlightShadowScale;

    return;

{

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
bool u_xlatb35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = abs(u_xlat16_32) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_22.y = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4 = max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4 = min(u_xlat16_4, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_4) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_14 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_31) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_22.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_4) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_22.x = clamp(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4 + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat30 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat30 = exp2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat4, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb35 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb35 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb35 = u_xlatb35 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_31 = (u_xlatb35) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_11 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_12 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat21;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTexShoe;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNrShoe;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
bool u_xlatb35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = abs(u_xlat16_32) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_22.y = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4 = max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4 = min(u_xlat16_4, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_4) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_14 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_31) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_4) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_22.x = clamp(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4 + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat30 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat30 = exp2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);

    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;

    u_xlat4.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat4, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb35 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb35 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb35 = u_xlatb35 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_31 = (u_xlatb35) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_17.xyz;

    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat0.x;

    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_11 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);

    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;

    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;

    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;

    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;

    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat21 = u_xlat21 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat21 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat9 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat21 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = max(u_xlat21, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat21 = inversesqrt(u_xlat21);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat21 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat21) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_6.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_6.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTexShoe;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNrShoe;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec4 u_xlat4;
mediump float u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump float u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
bool u_xlatb35;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat10.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_32 = abs(u_xlat16_32) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_22.y = min(u_xlat16_32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4 = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4 = max(u_xlat16_4, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4 = min(u_xlat16_4, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_4) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_14 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_14 = u_xlat16_4 * u_xlat16_4;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_14 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = float(1.0) / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat16_22.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_31) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_31 = min(max(u_xlat16_31, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_31 = clamp(u_xlat16_31, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_22.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat16_4) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_22.x = min(max(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_22.x = clamp(u_xlat16_22.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_31) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_14 / u_xlat30;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4 + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat30 = min(u_xlat30, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat30 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat30 = log2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat30 = exp2(u_xlat30);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat30 = min(max(u_xlat30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat30 = clamp(u_xlat30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat4.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_31 = dot(u_xlat4, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_31 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_12.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb35 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb35 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb35 = u_xlatb35 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_31 = (u_xlatb35) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_31) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat30) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = max(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat13 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat13) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_37 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_11 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_11;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_31 * u_xlat16_11 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_5.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_12 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_12;
    u_xlat16_12 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_12 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = max(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = min(u_xlat16_3.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
