void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_26 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_26) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = abs(u_xlat16_38) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_38 = min(u_xlat16_38, 1.0);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = clamp(u_xlat43, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_39)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_40;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_40 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_4 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat10_4.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = max(u_xlat16_42, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = log2(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_42 = exp2(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.x = log2(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat8.x = exp2(u_xlat8.x);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat41) * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32 + u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_26 / u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_14.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat20.x = min(u_xlat20.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat20.xxx;
    u_xlat20.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat13;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat37 + (-u_xlat41);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat37 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat24;
    u_xlat12 = 0.5 / u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat24 = (-u_xlat43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat24) * u_xlat36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_26);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat24 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb36 = u_xlat24<2.0;
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb36)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat24 + -2.0;
        u_xlat24 = (u_xlatb36) ? u_xlat24 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb24 = u_xlat24<1.0;
        u_xlat16_38 = (u_xlatb24) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati24 = int(u_xlat16_38);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).xyz;
        u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat37 = float(1.0) / u_xlat36;
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).y;
        u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat37;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).w;
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat16_14.x = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat8.x = log2(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat8.x = exp2(u_xlat8.x);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat41) * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32 + u_xlat20.x;

    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;

    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat20.x = min(u_xlat20.x, 100.0);

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);

    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;

    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_39;

    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_2.x));
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat37 + (-u_xlat41);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat37 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_14.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_14.x * 0.5;
    u_xlat24 = (-u_xlat43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat24) * u_xlat36 + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);

    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)

        u_xlatb36 = !!(u_xlat24<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb36 = u_xlat24<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb36)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;

        u_xlat24 = (u_xlatb36) ? u_xlat24 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb24 = !!(u_xlat24<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb24 = u_xlat24<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_38 = (u_xlatb24) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat37;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati24].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_38 = min(max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_38 = min(max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_26 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_26) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = abs(u_xlat16_38) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_38 = min(u_xlat16_38, 1.0);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = clamp(u_xlat43, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_39)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_40;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_40 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_4 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat10_4.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = max(u_xlat16_42, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = log2(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_42 = exp2(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.x = log2(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat8.x = exp2(u_xlat8.x);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat41) * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32 + u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_26 / u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_14.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat20.x = min(u_xlat20.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat20.xxx;
    u_xlat20.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat13;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat37 + (-u_xlat41);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat37 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat24;
    u_xlat12 = 0.5 / u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat24 = (-u_xlat43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat24) * u_xlat36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_26);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat24 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb36 = u_xlat24<2.0;
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb36)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat24 + -2.0;
        u_xlat24 = (u_xlatb36) ? u_xlat24 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb24 = u_xlat24<1.0;
        u_xlat16_38 = (u_xlatb24) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati24 = int(u_xlat16_38);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).xyz;
        u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat37 = float(1.0) / u_xlat36;
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).y;
        u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat37;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).w;
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati24).xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

};
#endif

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;

#else

    u_xlat16_42 = exp2(u_xlat16_42);

    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.x = log2(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat8.x = exp2(u_xlat8.x);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat41) * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32 + u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_26 / u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_14.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat20.x = min(u_xlat20.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat20.xxx;
    u_xlat20.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat8.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat13;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_39 = min(max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_39 = clamp(u_xlat16_39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39 + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_39 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_2.x));
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat37 + (-u_xlat41);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat41 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat37 / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * u_xlat16_14.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_14.x + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat12 + u_xlat24;
    u_xlat16_14.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_14.x * 0.5;
    u_xlat24 = (-u_xlat43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat24 * u_xlat24;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat36 * u_xlat24;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat24 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb36 = !!(u_xlat24<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb36 = u_xlat24<2.0;
#endif

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb24 = !!(u_xlat24<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb24 = u_xlat24<1.0;
#endif

        u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat37 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat37) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat37 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat36);
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat37;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati24].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_38 = min(max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat16_38;
        u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_38 = min(max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati24].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_1.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(u_xlat16_14.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_3.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_26 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = max(u_xlat36, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_26) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_14.x) + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat36) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = abs(u_xlat16_38) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_38 = min(u_xlat16_38, 1.0);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = clamp(u_xlat43, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_39 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 + u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_39)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_38) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat16_40 = (-u_xlat16_14.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_40;
    u_xlat16_40 = u_xlat16_40 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_4 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_40);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat10_4.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = max(u_xlat16_42, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = log2(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_42 = exp2(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.x = log2(u_xlat36);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat8.x = exp2(u_xlat8.x);
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat8.x + _ShadowOffset;

void main()
{

    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTexShoe;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNrShoe;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat9.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_29 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_29 = abs(u_xlat16_29) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_20.y = min(u_xlat16_29, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w * u_xlat16_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_13);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = (-u_xlat16_20.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_20.x = (-u_xlat16_28) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_20.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_20.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_20.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_20.x = min(max(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_28) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = inversesqrt(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat27 = min(max(u_xlat27, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat27) * u_xlat27 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat27 = min(max(u_xlat27, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat27 = log2(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat27 = exp2(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 + _ShadowOffset;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat27 = min(max(u_xlat27, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat12 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat12) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_10 * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_ATVECTOR_Y" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
Local Keywords { "_SHOEMODE_ON" }
"// hash: 3bd6c214ea0c5fe7
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump float _AddlightLerp;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat18;
float u_xlat19;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif

lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_BumpMapNrShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat9.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_29 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_29 = abs(u_xlat16_29) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_20.y = min(u_xlat16_29, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTexShoe, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * 6.0;

    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);

    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = (-u_xlat16_20.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_20.x = (-u_xlat16_28) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_20.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_20.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_20.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_28) + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = inversesqrt(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat27) * u_xlat27 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat27 = log2(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat27 = exp2(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat12 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat12) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_10 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy;
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.xz = exp2(u_xlat16_5.xz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = _AddlightLerp * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 5.0 + u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AddlightAttenuation;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
