void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat18 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat18 = max(u_xlat18, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat18);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat18) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat1.y * u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat8 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat18 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat3.y = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat8 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat3.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    u_xlat16_2 = u_xlat16_4.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_2;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2 * _SHColorScale;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xzw = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat0.xzw;
    u_xlat19 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat19 = max(u_xlat19, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat19);
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xzw * u_xlat1.xxx;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat0.y));
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainlightAttenuation;
    u_xlat16_5.z = u_xlat16_4.x * _RimlightAttenuation;

    vs_TEXCOORD8.y = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD8.w = 1.0;
    return;

uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
uniform 	mediump float _MetallicOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _ShadowOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _ShadowPow;
uniform 	mediump float _ShadowScale;
uniform 	vec4 _RimLightDir;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
uniform lowp samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec3 u_xlat0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
float u_xlat12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -2.0);
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_0.w + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(vec3(_NormalScale, _NormalScale, _NormalScale)) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot((-u_xlat9.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-u_xlat16_2.xxx) + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_29 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_29 = abs(u_xlat16_29) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_20.y = min(u_xlat16_29, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat10_0.w * u_xlat10_0.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_5 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_13);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = (-u_xlat16_20.y) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_20.x = (-u_xlat16_28) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = (-u_xlat16_20.yx) + vec2(1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_20.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_20.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_28) + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = inversesqrt(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.x = (-u_xlat27) * u_xlat27 + 1.0;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27 + u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_13 / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat3.x = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat3.x;
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 100.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat3.xzw;
    u_xlat27 = log2(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * _ShadowPow;
    u_xlat27 = exp2(u_xlat27);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 + _ShadowOffset;
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xzw = u_xlat3.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(_ShadowScale));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat3.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD8.yyy * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat12 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat12) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_2.x / u_xlat16_28;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_7.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_10 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
}

 Pass {
  Name "OUTLINE"
  LOD 300
  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "AdvancedOutline" "RenderPipeline" = "LightweightPipeline" "RenderType" = "[_RenderType]" }
  GpuProgramID 66383
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_OFF" }
"// hash: 413c87d8e433ee1b
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat1.ww;
    gl_Position.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = 0.00999999978 / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.w = u_xlat1.w;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
void main()

    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = clamp(u_xlat9, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;

    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat1.ww;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;

	UNITY_UNIFORM float _NearWidth;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat9 = min(max(u_xlat9, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat9 = clamp(u_xlat9, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat1.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);

    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat1.ww;
    gl_Position.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = 0.00999999978 / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.w = u_xlat1.w;
    return;
}

#endif

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1

#else

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)

#endif

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;

in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec3 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump float u_xlat16_3;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.zxy * in_TANGENT0.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yzx * in_TANGENT0.zxy + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_TANGENT0.www;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * unity_WorldTransformParams.www;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.yyy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_TANGENT0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat12 = min(max(u_xlat12, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat12 = clamp(u_xlat12, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat1.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3 = max(u_xlat2.w, 0.200000003);
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_3 * 0.00999999978;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat8 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat8 = inversesqrt(u_xlat8);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat8) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;

    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);

    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];

    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _LightDirection.xyz * _ShadowBias.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _BaseColor;
uniform 	mediump float _Cutoff;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BaseMap;
varying highp vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
#define SV_TARGET0 gl_FragData[0]
lowp float u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_BaseMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).w;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat10_0 * _BaseColor.w + (-_Cutoff);
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    SV_TARGET0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
"

"// hash: a4b062e28e4664dd
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 300 es

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 _ShadowBias;
uniform 	vec3 _LightDirection;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _BaseMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BaseColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OcclusionStrength;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
float u_xlat6;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _LightDirection.xyz * _ShadowBias.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat6 = min(max(u_xlat6, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif

{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BaseMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).w;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_0 * _BaseColor.w + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1<0.0;

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _BaseMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BaseColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OcclusionStrength;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _BaseMap;
in highp vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_TARGET0;
mediump float u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BaseMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).w;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_0 * _BaseColor.w + (-_Cutoff);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    SV_TARGET0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
